# This is a shared default backend you can't modify the code for.
# In order to create your own backend, run `npx convex dev`.
VITE_CONVEX_URL=https://laudable-anaconda-558.convex.cloud

# Clerk publishable key (sign-in, pricing pages, checkout UI)
VITE_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=

# Server-side env vars — set in Convex dashboard, NOT in .env.local:
#   CLERK_SECRET_KEY        — Clerk admin API
#   CLERK_JWT_ISSUER_DOMAIN — Clerk issuer for JWT verification
#   CLERK_WEBHOOK_SECRET    — Svix signing secret for the /webhooks/clerk endpoint.
#                             Get it from Clerk dashboard → Webhooks → your endpoint
#                             → Signing Secret. Format: whsec_...
#   CLERK_ADMIN_USER_IDS    — Comma-separated list of Clerk user_xxx IDs that get
#                             admin-tier access in queries/mutations. Action-tier
#                             admin gating uses publicMetadata.role === 'admin'.
#   BILLING_ENABLED         — Server-side enforcement kill switch (instant, no rebuild).
#                             Defaults OFF — must be set to 'true' in prod or every
#                             paid feature is un-gated. See env-setup.md.
#   BILLING_TRUST_CACHE     — Operator-only kill switch. Set to 'true' during a
#                             confirmed Clerk API outage to trust cached plans for
#                             up to 4h past syncedAt. Revert as soon as Clerk
#                             recovers. Never leave enabled permanently.
#
#   FAL_KEY                 — fal.ai API key for image generation + vision.
#   FIRECRAWL_API_KEY       — Firecrawl API key for URL-import scraping.
#
#   R2_ENDPOINT             — Cloudflare R2 endpoint, e.g. https://<accountid>.r2.cloudflarestorage.com
#   R2_ACCESS_KEY_ID        — R2 S3-compatible access key id
#   R2_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY    — R2 S3-compatible secret access key
#   R2_BUCKET_NAME          — R2 bucket name where uploaded assets live
#   R2_PUBLIC_URL           — Public CDN URL for the bucket (e.g. https://pub-xxx.r2.dev or custom domain)
#
# Dev-only — NEVER set in prod:
#   CONVEX_TEST_MODE        — when 'true', mocks bypass real APIs (testMocks.ts).
